data.description: Well maintained home with roof having been replaced in 2018.All tile throughout and rear yard fenced with huge, oversized Lanai. Split floor plan with main bedroom on one side of the house and the rest on the other side. Updated kitchen with quartz counter tops and soft close cabinets and drawers. Inside laundry, remodeled main bathroom. House comes with hurricane shutters and rear slider impact glass and kitchen window. House is not in a flood zone, close to shops and schools and more. Easy to show.
